I" <p>Preliminary release notes for the 1.0 release of OpenPOTD.</p>

<p>Multiserver:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Allow different servers to add OpenPOTD at the same time.</li>
  <li>Allow custom prefixes to be set.</li>
  <li>Allow servers to set their own gold/silver/bronze roles.</li>
</ul>

<p>Other:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Allow people to toggle anonymity on the OpenPOTD website.</li>
  <li>Custom menus implementation works in DMs as well.</li>
  <li>Added exponential cooldown system for not solving a problem.</li>
  <li>Add a license (AGPL 3.0).</li>
</ul>
